# English-Only Subsite

This project is a single-route English subsite for toolcore. All user-facing copy must stay in English.

## Language

- Default UI language is English (`config.LANG = 'en'`). Do not switch the default to another locale.
- Do not add Chinese (or other non-English) text to HTML, SEO meta tags, footer links, or custom UI strings.
- Translation files (for example `src/js/languages/zh.json`) may exist for optional user language switching, but must not be used for default subsite branding or SEO.

## Footer

- Keep a static footer link to `https://toolcore.dev/`.
- Footer link text must be English only (for example `toolcore.dev` or `Visit toolcore.dev`).
- Do not use Chinese labels such as `е®ҳзҪ‘`.

## SEO (single route)

- Maintain English SEO in `index.html` for the one public route (`/`).
- Keep `title`, `description`, `keywords`, `canonical`, Open Graph, Twitter, and JSON-LD in English.
- Keep `robots.txt` and `sitemap.xml` aligned with the same canonical URL.

